ng it into a viable building option.</span></p>\n<p><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/eP0EGgU.png\" width=\"1344\" height=\"48\" /></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\"><strong>📦 Cross-Compatibility:</strong></span></p>\n<ul>\n<li><a title=\"Boatload\" href=\"https://modrinth.com/mod/boatload\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">Boatload</span></a></li>\n<li><a title=\"Buzzier Bees\" href=\"https://modrinth.com/mod/buzzier-bees\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">Buzzier Bees</span></a></li>\n<li><a title=\"Quark\" href=\"https://modrinth.com/mod/quark\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">Quark</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n<p><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/eP0EGgU.png\" width=\"1344\" height=\"48\" /></p>\n<p><a title=\"Nodecraft\" href=\"https://nodecraft.com/r/abnormals\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/oZS1R9g.png\" width=\"1280\" height=\"184\" /></a></p>",
